description: XcelPlus International, Inc. distributes chemicals, lubricants, and alternative fuel technologies in the United States. It offers products in the areas of automotive, aviation, marine, emissions, lawn and garden, heavy duty equipment, industrial heavy duty equipment, agricultural, mission critical, railway, and miscellaneous. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Saluda, Virginia. XcelPlus International, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of Clean Energy Pathways, Inc.
